descriptionHtml:
Knowing yourself is the first step to change, RunningQuotient helps you easily achieve this.

【Running Analysis】
Help you evaluate the performance of your running ability(run level), knowing your own running changes, and provide the most suitable pace zone for your scientific training.

【Pressure calculation】
Visualize the training pressure index every time when you upload training record. Through this training index, you can master your own schedule and avoid overtraining.

【Grasp the situation】
Based on all your previous training records, analyze your current physical, fatigue and conditional indicators to help you get the personal best.

【Attention to technology】
Running technology is important but easily ignore, through the data you will understand your technical indicators under each pace zone, help you run faster, farther, less vulnerable.

Customer Service: support@runningquotient.com
descriptionShort: Bring you into scientific training and enhance running performance.

creator: 永動科技股份有限公司
descriptionHtml:
Knowing yourself is the first step to change, RunningQuotient helps you easily achieve this.

【Running Analysis】
Help you evaluate the performance of your running ability(run level), knowing your own running changes, and provide the most suitable pace zone for your scientific training.

【Pressure calculation】
Visualize the training pressure index every time when you upload training record. Through this training index, you can master your own schedule and avoid overtraining.

【Grasp the situation】
Based on all your previous training records, analyze your current physical, fatigue and conditional indicators to help you get the personal best.

【Attention to technology】
Running technology is important but easily ignore, through the data you will understand your technical indicators under each pace zone, help you run faster, farther, less vulnerable.

Access location information description:
RunningQuotient collects location information in the background when you enable the running feature so that it can be displayed on the map when the application is closed or not in use, and can also be used to record the path of your run and stop collecting location information when you finish your run.

Customer Service: support@runningquotient.com
